# Line-ending policy: this repo is edited on Windows but built and tested on
# Linux and macOS. Shell scripts and the Makefile MUST be LF -- bash chokes on
# a CR in the shebang/lines, and make mishandles CRLF in recipes.
*.sh   text eol=lf
Makefile text eol=lf

# Let git normalize other text files to LF in the repo (checked out per-OS).
* text=auto
